{"tid":2170801,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"赤柱監獄懲教助理涉交囚犯資料予親友　被廉署拘捕及停職","createTime":"2020-08-23T13:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T14:00:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa264acff2e9e80786ba176d1a151a526c765d28","tid":2170801,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"懲教署轄下赤柱監獄一名懲教助理，涉嫌將在囚人士的資料提供予其任職紀律部隊的親友，已被廉政公署拘捕，期後被懲教署停職。廉署表示，根據政策，該署一般不會評論個別事件。根據廉署的法定職責，若接獲貪污投訴，如有足夠資料，廉署必定會按既定程序依法跟進。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，被停職的一級懲教助理姓李，駐守赤柱監獄。廉署早前接獲舉報，指有人涉嫌將在囚人士的資料提供予其任職紀律部隊的親友，涉公職人員行為失當，廉署經調查後，於本月中將他拘捕，於本月18日被懲教署停職。<br />\n<br />\nsource:  東網"},{"pid":"9ceb9e2b00bb2bb17538ba6316cee6364a803245","tid":2170801,"uid":221171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyAn2nt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyAn2nt.jpg&h=7fcace64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TY8XVP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TY8XVP.png&h=29469d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vxmyua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vxmyua.jpg&h=0994bc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtgeTua.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtgeTua.png&h=e51b0323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另支持香港戰狼黃景樂出征南海<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZR72hVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZR72hVR.jpg&h=0d988271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDxUTub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDxUTub.jpg&h=68e3f2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhoMKAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhoMKAS.jpg&h=92993610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0096d74cdf86a741f9f980438b6